        <Parent_String>vegetable adhesive [300014827], organic adhesive [300014809], adhesive by composition or origin [300014804], adhesive [300014801], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
